	(836, 2, '2013-02-11 09:17:48', '2013-02-11 17:17:48', '<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/f2a73b7d88bdd820536e7f658ba89fd8/tumblr_inline_mi2fsnNKDR1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p><img src="http://media.tumblr.com/4ba5cb67d8ef2d4b5d8049de859f3141/tumblr_inline_mi2fsyjtsw1qz4rgp.png"/></p>\n\n<p>The Enclothed team believes that every man deserves the softest tshirt possible. Whilst most high-end tshirts that feel softer than cashmere when slipped on, their price tags are sometimes daunting. Enter the Collective tshirts: premium, undeniably soft and comfortable with versatile fits and cuts, ranging from £45 - £60. </p>\n<p><strong>QUICK FACTS</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Undeniably one of the softest T-shirts Enclothed has come across.</li>\n<li>Great fit.</li>\n<li>Ethically sourced.</li>\n<li>Premium quality without the premium price tag.</li>\n<li>The Collective collaborated with iconic photographers Bob Carlos Clarke and Terry O’Neill producing thought provoking and insipiring tshirts.</li>\n<li>Also found in: Harvey Nichols, Cruise, Flannels and other premium boutiques and stores.</li>\n</ul>', 'New arrivals - The Collective', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'new-arrivals-the-collective', '', '', '2013-02-11 09:17:48', '2013-02-11 17:17:48', '', 0, 'http://enclothedblog.tumblr.com/post/42850450974', 0, 'post', '', 0),
