ut not limited to, reasonable administrative and legal costs) resulting from the breach.</li>\r\n	<li>Further legal action against you.</li>\r\n	<li>Disclosure of such information to law enforcement authorities as we reasonably feel is necessary.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe exclude liability for actions taken in response to breaches of this acceptable use policy. The responses described in this policy are not limited, and we may take any other action we reasonably deem appropriate.\r\n<h3>23. YOUR CONCERNS</h3>\r\nIf you have any concerns about material which appears on our site, please contact us by email at help@enclothed.co.ukh3\r\n\r\n[/fullwidth_text]', 'Terms & Conditions', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'terms-conditions', '', '', '2014-04-17 16:31:00', '2014-04-17 16:31:00', '', 0, 'http://enclothed.dev/?page_id=858', 0, 'page', '', 0),
