	(882, 6, '2014-04-08 09:50:53', '2014-04-08 09:50:53', 'Buying smart trainers can be a minefield. You want something good quality, smart that you can wear to the office on a Friday, that goes with chinos or dark jeans and that will last you well.\r\n\r\nImportant factors are comfort and durability. Look for a sturdy but soft leather upper which has good strong double stitching, a firm rubber sole and well fitted eyelets.\r\n\r\nA smart trainer will normally come in beige, black, brown or dark colours but you can add a flash of colour with stitching or laces.\r\n\r\nWe are particular fans of Thorocraft’ s smart trainers.  Sturdy, stylish and something a little different. <a href="http://www.thorocraft.com/">http://www.thorocraft.com/</a>', 'Smart Trainers', 'You want something good quality, smart that you can wear to the office on a Friday, that goes with chinos or dark jeans and that will last you well.', 'trash', 'closed', 'open', '', 'smart-trainers', '', '', '2014-04-17 16:31:03', '2014-04-17 16:31:03', '', 0, 'http://enclothed.dev/?p=882', 0, 'post', '', 0),
