	(620, 1, '2014-03-26 18:03:24', '2014-03-26 18:03:24', '[spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3" el_position="first"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="http://enclothed.dev/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tshirts.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000;">T-SHIRTS</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #f7b666;">£25 - £70</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The staple element of a man\'s wardrobe. We\'ve got tees, polo\'s, v-necks, crew-necks. All your basic needs.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="http://enclothed.dev/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/shirts.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000;">SHIRTS</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #f7b666;">£60 - £100</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Formal, casual Friday, linens for holidays, a well fitted button up shirt is an essential. Casual or smart - we have it.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3" el_position="last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/blazers.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000;">BLAZERS</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #f7b666;">£25 - £70</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Very few items are as sophisticated yet versatile as a blazer. Casual fabric to smart tailored, we have types for any occasion.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_parallax parallax_type="image" bg_type="cover" parallax_video_height="video-height" parallax_video_overlay="none" parallax_image_height="content-height" parallax_image_movement="fixed" parallax_image_speed="0.5" alt_background="none" el_class="grey_bg" width="1/1" el_position="first last"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000; line-height: 34px;">WHEN DO I PAY</span></p>\r\n<img class="size-full aligncenter" alt="line" src="/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/line.png" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Ever heard of try then buy? You enter your credit card details when you order a box but you\r\ndon\'t pay until you\'ve received it all and decided what you want to keep.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Once your box has arrived you have 10 days to try everything on. What you like you keep.\r\nWhat you don\'t we collect. We will only charge you for what you keep.</p>\r\n[/spb_parallax] [spb_text_block pb_margin_bottom="no" pb_border_bottom="no" width="1/3" el_position="first"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-515" alt="tshirts" src="http://enclothed.dev/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/jackets.png" width="322" height="274" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 3px; font-size: 30px;"><span style="color: #000;">T-SHIRTS</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center; font-family: proxbold; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: #f7b666;">£75 - £2070</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">The right jacket can change an outfit entirely. From suede to hooded, we\'ve got it all.</p>\r\n[/spb_text_block] [spb_text_block